snippet.title: Undertale Icebound Trailer - UNDEREVENT 2023
snippet.description:
IF YOU HAVEN'T ALREADY, GO WATCH UNDEREVENT 2023!!!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ansCGZUhtVk

This is it, this is what we've been cooking up these last couple months! Consider this an early Xmas gift from the Icebox team. We couldn't have made it to this point without your support! We're ever so thankful everyone chose to stick around with us and see things through. We're still miles away from a full release, but sit tight and we'll be at the finish line in no time. As a bonus, we've released 8 new tracks, 2 of which are early versions of 2 of the new releases. We hope you like them! Thanks for all the support and we'll see you starside! 

CHECK OUT THE LATEST DEVLOG!!! 
https://gamejolt.com/p/devlog-4-underevent-xmas-special-mikbaanq

Support the people who helped make this possible:
https://soundcloud.com/mr-coffee-dude
https://twitter.com/Kekuus07
https://www.deviantart.com/edgytalesans
https://www.deviantart.com/piesprite
https://www.deviantart.com/hollow-sufferings
https://www.deviantart.com/4dtoast
https://twitter.com/That_OneZalGuy (Contributer)
https://www.deviantart.com/edgytalesans (Contributer)
??? (Team member wished to remain anonymous)

Listen to the OST here:
https://soundcloud.com/undertaleiceboundofficial
https://soundcloud.com/chione-ivins (Cut Content Archive)

Play the Undertale Icebound Demo here:
gamejolt.com/games/undertaleicebound/688804

Undertale Icebound directed/written by Lucana.dll, co-directed by __b:
twitter.com/lucanaforever
twitter.com/__b_dot_stuff
